ost NBA-laden rosters at the Olympics, led by legendary Australian coach Brian Goorjian, and as a country that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s known for shining at the Olympics we expect Australia to be one of the two teams that prevail out of the group of death.\\u00c2 They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve got talent and their biggest issue at last summer\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s FIBA World Cup was lack of size, but the additions of Landale and Magnay - who is receiving interest from NBA teams - address that issue.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1576, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Goorjian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brian Goorjian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Goorjian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Goorjian\"}, {\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4551883295998424e-119, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeman_Dyson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.089342567119102e-18, \"text\": \"Dyson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeman_Dyson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeman_Dyson\"}, {\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dante_Exum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dante Exum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dante_Exum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dante_Exum\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"