m\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5745}, {\"ngram\": \"Giannis\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Greek freak is capable of lifting this group to victory against almost anyone, but he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll still need help from their supporting cast.\", \"from\": 5788, \"to\": 5926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5792, \"end\": 5797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999042885142109, \"rank\": 9.572064650369533e-05, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 5826, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 5840, \"to\": 5847}, {\"ngram\": \"almost anyone\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5869}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 5894, \"to\": 5898}, {\"ngram\": \"their supporting cast\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greece qualified via the Olympic Qualifying tournaments played in early July and Spanoulis went with a starting unit of Walkup, Calathes, Papanikolaou, Giannis, and Papagiannis.\\u00c2 That five formed an impressive defensive base for them to build on.\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 6174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5927, \"end\": 5933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999114479617, \"rank\": 8.855165259697915e-08, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Qualifying tournaments\", \"from\": 5948, \"to\": 5982}, {\"ngram\": \"early July\", \"from\": 5993, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"Spanoulis\", \"from\": 6008, \"to\": 6017}, {\"ngram\": \"a starting unit\", \"from\": 6028, \"to\": 6043}, {\"ngram\": \"Walkup\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6053}, {\"ngram\": \"Calathes\", \"from\": 6055, \"to\": 6063}, {\"ngram\": \"Papanikolaou\", \"from\": 6065, \"to\": 6077}, {\"ngram\": \"Giannis\", \"from\": 6079, \"to\": 6086}, {\"ngram\": \"Papagiannis\", \"from\": 6092, \"to\": 6103}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6105}, {\"ngram\": \"an impressive defensive base\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Calathes and Walkup are two guards who are elite defenders for their position, and capable of switching onto bigger opponents.\", \"from\": 6175, \"to\": 6301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6188, \"end\": 6194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Walkup\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Calathes\", \"from\": 6175, \"to\": 6183}, {\"ngram\": \"two guards\", \"from\": 6199, \"to\": 6209}, {\"ngram\": \"elite defenders\", \"from\": 6218, \"to\": 6233}, {\"ngram\": \"their position\", \"from\": 6238, \"to\": 6252}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger opponents\", \"from\": 6284, \"to\": 6300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Papanikolaou offers more of the same, Giannis is, well, Giannis, and Papagiannis helps provide size on the backboards.\", \"from\": 6302, \"to\": 6420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Papanikolaou\", \"from\": 6302, \"to\": 6314}, {\"ngram\": \"Giannis\", \"from\": 6340, \"to\": 6347}, {\"ngram\": \"Giannis\", \"from\": 6358, \"to\": 6365}, {\"ngram\": \"Papagiannis\", \"from\": 6371, \"to\": 6382}, {\"ngram\": \"size\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6401}, {\"ngram\": \"the backboards\", \"from\": 6405, \"to\": 6419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In their game against Luka Doncic\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Slovenia, there was not one player in this five-man group that Doncic could target.\", \"from\": 6421, \"to\": 6542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6459, \"end\": 6467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.110903016517886e-23, \"text\": \"Slovenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 6424, \"to\": 6434}, {\"ngram\": \"one player\", \"from\": 6483, \"to\": 6493}, {\"ngram\": \"this five-man group\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6516}, {\"ngram\": \"Doncic\", \"from\": 6522, \"to\": 6528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It completely shut down Slovenia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s offense and was truly the strongest a Giannis team has ever looked in international play.\\u00c2 The offense is another question.\", \"from\": 6543, \"to\": 6704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Slovenia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s offense\", \"from\": 6567, \"to\": 6587}, {\"ngram\": \"a Giannis team\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6630}, {\"ngram\": \"international play\", \"from\": 6650, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6669, \"to\": 6670}, {\"ngram\": \"The offense\", \"from\": 6671, \"to\": 6682}, {\"ngram\": \"another question\", \"from\": 6686, \"to\": 6702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the defensive fortitude created by Spanoulis\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 optimal starting five, the offense is far from convincing.\", \"from\": 6705, \"to\": 6815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the defensive fortitude\", \"from\": 6709, \"to\": 6732}, {\"ngram\": \"Spanoulis\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 optimal starting\", \"from\": 6744, \"to\": 6773}, {\"ngram\": \"the offense\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Calathes and Walkup are not shooting threats.\", \"from\": 6816, \"to\": 6861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6829, \"end\": 6835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Walkup\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Walkup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Calathes\", \"from\": 6816, \"to\": 6824}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 6853, \"to\": 6860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They can make open threes, but not nearly enough to warrant a defenders full attention.\", \"from\": 6862, \"to\": 6949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"open threes\", \"from\": 6876, \"to\": 6887}, {\"ngram\": \"a defenders\", \"from\": 6922, \"to\": 6933}, {\"ngram\": \"full attention\", \"from\": 6934, \"to\": 6948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Papanikolaou is slightly better and Papagiannis and backup big Mitoglou honestly have a claim for best shooters on the squad.\", \"from\": 6950, \"to\": 7075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Papanikolaou\", \"from\": 6950, \"to\": 6962}, {\"ngram\": \"Papagiannis\", \"from\": 6986, \"to\": 6997}, {\"ngram\": \"backup big Mitoglou\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7021}, {\"ngram\": \"a claim\", \"from\": 7036, \"to\": 7043}, {\"ngram\": \"best shooters\", \"from\": 7048, \"to\": 7061}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 7065, \"to\": 7074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The paint will be clogged for Giannis, he will see multiple defenders constantly, and be very dependent on his teammates providing some outlier shooting.\\u00c2 Greece\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s path to maybe reaching the semifinals and thus, a medal game - which would be their ceiling this summer - will be to keep games as lowscoring as possible.\", \"from\": 7076, \"to\": 7397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The paint\", \"from\": 7076, \"to\": 7085}, {\"ngram\": \"Giannis\", \"from\": 7106, \"to\": 7113}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple defenders\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7145}, {\"ngram\": \"his teammates\", \"from\": 7183, 