\": \"the Qualifying tournament\", \"from\": 8693, \"to\": 8718}, {\"ngram\": \"an underwhelming showing\", \"from\": 8725, \"to\": 8749}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 FIBA World Cup\", \"from\": 8753, \"to\": 8776}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear sign\", \"from\": 8781, \"to\": 8793}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite\", \"from\": 8828, \"to\": 8837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being drawn into the group of death puts them on the outside looking in.\\u00c2 Don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t expect Spain to be like this for long.\", \"from\": 8839, \"to\": 8960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8929, \"end\": 8934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9020875945645466e-18, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 8856, \"to\": 8865}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 8869, \"to\": 8874}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 8888, \"to\": 8899}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 8911, \"to\": 8920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldama and Garuba are still young, Juan Nunez was a highly sought-after second-round prospect in the 2024 NBA Draft, and Real Madrid youngster Hugo Gonazlez is a projected top-5 pick in the loaded 2025 class.\", \"from\": 8961, \"to\": 9169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8961, \"end\": 8967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7770116637181646e-31, \"text\": \"Aldama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Aldama\"}, {\"begin\": 9082, \"end\": 9093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_Baloncesto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6599929890264366e-17, \"text\": \"Real Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_Baloncesto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_Baloncesto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Garuba\", \"from\": 8972, \"to\": 8978}, {\"ngram\": \"Juan Nunez\", \"from\": 8996, \"to\": 9006}, {\"ngram\": \"a highly sought-after second-round prospect\", \"from\": 9011, \"to\": 9054}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 NBA Draft\", \"from\": 9058, \"to\": 9076}, {\"ngram\": \"a projected top-5 pick\", \"from\": 9121, \"to\": 9143}, {\"ngram\": \"the loaded 2025 class\", \"from\": 9147, \"to\": 9168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This Olympics will be a swan song for Fernandez, who is appearing in his record-setting sixth Olympics, and four years from now this squad will look very different, and likely much better.\\u00c2 Head Coach:Aleksandar \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAco\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Petrovic NBA Players:Gui Santos Remaining Roster:Marcelinho Huertas, Yago Dos Santos, Bruno Caboclo, Didi Louzada, Cristiano Felicio, Georginho De Paula, Lucas Dias, Vitor Benite, Alexey Borges, Elinho Corazza, and Leo Meindl Do we expect them to advance?Yes - 3rd Why or why not?Aco Petrovic, the older brother of the late Drazen Petrovic, is back in charge of the Brazil men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national team and while they don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t boast NBA rotation players such as Leandro Barbosa and Tiago Splitter like they used to, this squad can still be a thorn in everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s side.\\u00c2 With three elite pick-and-roll point guards in Dos Santos, Neto, and the 41-year-old former Los Angeles Lakers guard Marcelinho Huertas to pair with quality roll-men Caboclo or Felicio this Brazil squad can regularly generate decent looks in the half-court.\", \"from\": 9170, \"to\": 10217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9403, \"end\": 9406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4551883295998424e-119, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"t