 {\"ngram\": \"their perimeter defense\", \"from\": 16566, \"to\": 16589}, {\"ngram\": \"a true weakness\", \"from\": 16593, \"to\": 16608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Micic and Bogdanovic are high-level guards but both can be targeted at the other end.\", \"from\": 16610, \"to\": 16695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Micic\", \"from\": 16610, \"to\": 16615}, {\"ngram\": \"Bogdanovic\", \"from\": 16620, \"to\": 16630}, {\"ngram\": \"high-level guards\", \"from\": 16635, \"to\": 16652}, {\"ngram\": \"the other end\", \"from\": 16681, \"to\": 16694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same can be said for Guduric.\\u00c2 That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s why an upset victory over Team USA will need a small dose of America beating themselves.\", \"from\": 16696, \"to\": 16829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16767, \"end\": 16775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9901083303131466e-41, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guduric\", \"from\": 16721, \"to\": 16728}, {\"ngram\": \"an upset victory\", \"from\": 16744, \"to\": 16760}, {\"ngram\": \"a small dose\", \"from\": 16785, \"to\": 16797}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 16801, \"to\": 16808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia can hang offensively with their starting group but can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t compete with Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s bench, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll need that group to go cold to have a real chance.\\u00c2 With the best player in the world in Jokic and a microwave scorer like Bogdanovic, anything is possible, but this squad has a notable weakness that they won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be able to overcome without some luck.\", \"from\": 16830, \"to\": 17190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16830, \"end\": 16836, \"tit