3, \"to\": 17270}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Head Coach\", \"from\": 17290, \"to\": 17302}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 JT Thor\", \"from\": 17326, \"to\": 17335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do we expect them to advance?No - 3rd Why or why not?It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hard to truly assess this South Sudan team.\", \"from\": 17678, \"to\": 17782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3rd\", \"from\": 17712, \"to\": 17715}, {\"ngram\": \"not?It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 17727, \"to\": 17737}, {\"ngram\": \"this South Sudan team\", \"from\": 17759, \"to\": 17780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are very much a case of building the plane while it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s flying, a task former Chicago Bull Luol Deng has undertaken with great pride and quite successfully as they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve qualified for the Olympics for the first time in their country's short-lived history.\\u00c2 There are no real expectations for South Sudan this summer, being there is an achievement in itself.\", \"from\": 17783, \"to\": 18145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17866, \"end\": 17878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chicago Bull\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago_Bulls\"}, {\"begin\": 17879, \"end\": 17888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luol Deng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 17802, \"to\": 17808}, {\"ngram\": \"the plane\", \"from\": 17821, \"to\": 17830}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 17837, \"to\": 17843}, {\"ngram\": \"a task\", \"from\": 17852, \"to\": 17858}, {\"ngram\": \"great pride\", \"from\": 17909, \"to\": 17920}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 17947, \"to\": 17956}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 17971, \"to\": 17983}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 17988, \"to\": 18002}, {\"ngram\": \"their country's short-lived history\", \"from\": 18006, \"to\": 18041}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 18042, \"to\": 18043}, {\"ngram\": \"no real expectations\", \"from\": 18054, \"to\": 18074}, {\"ngram\": \"South Sudan\", \"from\": 18079, \"to\": 18090}, {\"ngram\": \"an achievement\", \"from\": 18119, \"to\": 18133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anything else is a luxury.\", \"from\": 18146, \"to\": 18172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anything\", \"from\": 18146, \"to\": 18154}, {\"ngram\": \"a luxury\", \"from\": 18163, \"to\": 18171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But their narrow one-point loss in a warm-up match against Team USA, which called on the Los Angeles Lakers forward to completely take the game over, was a flex and lesson for the world that this group does have elite talent and two-way athleticism.\\u00c2 Jones and Shayok bring the half-court creation necessary, and the addition of NBL wings like Majok Deng and Bul Kuol provides that two-way play alongside Hornets wing JT Thor.\", \"from\": 18173, \"to\": 18600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18232, \"end\": 18240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9901083303131466e-41, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 18262, \"end\": 18280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.089838212468113e-167, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Lakers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_La