5}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 19406, \"to\": 19420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Particularly with the addition of Joel Embiid, Team USA finally has an answer for anything and everything that may be thrown at them this summer.\", \"from\": 19439, \"to\": 19584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19473, \"end\": 19484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joel Embiid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\"}, {\"begin\": 19486, \"end\": 19494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9901083303131466e-41, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the addition\", \"from\": 19457, \"to\": 19469}, {\"ngram\": \"an answer\", \"from\": 19507, \"to\": 19516}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 19521, \"to\": 19529}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 19534, \"to\": 19544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The days of needing someone like Javale McGee are long gone and now - they can win playing any style necessary.\\u00c2 Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest concern will be if their bench goes cold in a key game.\", \"from\": 19585, \"to\": 19775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19618, \"end\": 19630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JaVale_McGee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javale McGee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JaVale_McGee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JaVale_McGee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The days\", \"from\": 19585, \"to\": 19593}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 19605, \"to\": 19612}, {\"ngram\": \"any style\", \"from\": 19676, \"to\": 19685}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest concern\", \"from\": 19696, \"to\": 19726}, {\"ngram\": \"their bench\", \"from\": 19738, \"to\": 19749}, {\"ngram\": \"a key game\", \"from\": 19763, \"to\": 19773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As other countries have improved at basketball over the past few decades, many are capable of putting together starting fives that can hang with Team USA: Australia, Canada, France, Germany, and Serbia can all stay competitive through a quarter and even a half of high-level hoops.\", \"from\": 19776, \"to\": 20057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19921, \"end\": 19929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9901083303131466e-41, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 19931, \"end\": 19940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9935636822109177, \"rank\": 0.0064779951901544576, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 19942, \"end\": 19948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9998044422072514, \"rank\": 0.0001945117657082621, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 19950, \"end\": 19956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.006956583523335e-21, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24