175, \"to\": 20184}, {\"ngram\": \"All-NBA talent\", \"from\": 20189, \"to\": 20203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s where they can pull away and put a game to bed.\\u00c2 Should this group go cold, suffer injuries, or simply run into a shortened rotation that can come close to gutting out a full game against them then that is where we will see this group truly get tested.\", \"from\": 20236, \"to\": 20498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 20278, \"to\": 20284}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 20288, \"to\": 20291}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 20292, \"to\": 20293}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 20301, \"to\": 20311}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 20328, \"to\": 20336}, {\"ngram\": \"a shortened rotation\", \"from\": 20357, \"to\": 20377}, {\"ngram\": \"a full game\", \"from\": 20413, \"to\": 20424}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 20469, \"to\": 20479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This Team USA squad does not have a weakness, but they could suffer from misfortune and spiral into their demise.\", \"from\": 20499, \"to\": 20612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20504, \"end\": 20512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9901083303131466e-41, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a weakness\", \"from\": 20533, \"to\": 20543}, {\"ngram\": \"misfortune\", \"from\": 20572, \"to\": 20582}, {\"ngram\": \"their demise\", \"from\": 20599, \"to\": 20611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the doomsday scenario but as long as they avoid that, they should leave France with gold medals around their neck.\\u00c2 There will be a seeded draw for the quarterfinals, with the eight teams placed into four, two-team pots.